  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-921c16bd-9838-4eaf-bd56-186c48d89e6d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223527277823/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-84d25f91-54df-4358-9689-3d524b907443\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-50edb1b9-8de7-4925-b529-1769e4beb6be\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3be973bf-bf73-4947-ae35-bea2ba707759\" style=\"color:#555555;\">프로필 명함이 가장 돋보이는 업종은 무엇일까? 그것은 자신의 경력과 신상을 홍보하는 업종일 겁니다. 이 부분에서 가장 많이 사용되는 업종이 아마도 PT 트레이너일겁니다. PT 트레이너는 자신의 보디 프로필을 찍으면서도 고객에게 자신의 경력을 어필해야 하는 피트니스센터에서도 중요한 역할을 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f92beaf1-4317-4913-a3e4-093e88f70723\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-077d760d-365f-441c-bc96-370962943d37\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-74ebf1ad-8d42-4635-abf4-fd4f26c515f7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-65071ec7-d10a-4477-8a8d-39c7dbe02836\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 때문에 보디 프로필을 촬영하고 가게 앞 배너나 명함에 소개 이미지를 업로드합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-c5b6f78e-3aa2-46ee-ac0c-bde3807c8302\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223527277823/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223527277823/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223527277823/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb1564f0-c27e-459b-bb6b-b135c9f84bd3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f5ba608f-46fb-49ec-871c-ffc1e49b5aa7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-59db709d-6c47-418a-b4c7-f1bd39d2e532\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4a7f5666-b767-4d68-9c2b-36ff2eba7d60\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-aa9225d6-c687-4c52-9d6e-0a0bf4d25490\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>가장 저렴한 가격에 프로필 명함을 제작해 드리고 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0340fefd-f299-4c9b-a6d3-223944ae9fe5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8555a96a-6d1e-48c0-ac5e-716324ecd0cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-901bf682-c476-4f05-9d08-ac3d47d24de6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-373cecef-e8fe-48d0-a7bd-7ccc10bb7c55\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 PT 템플릿으로 작업하는 경우는 정해진 내용을 주셔야 작업이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-78e82ee1-15d7-49a5-bc4a-89719f032d0d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3fa7b758-b8f0-4750-ad73-68fbc523f703\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내용은 다음과 같은 내용으로 정의됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3c492b91-798e-4aea-9c52-4aebd37adfd6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-37a532e1-c3b5-4ae2-84a9-7fce9850f81c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d13d0623-94c2-4373-a60d-7043a426a9ef\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223527277823/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f76c20a5-7039-4f1b-b236-1e1a3f4501b1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c46ac024-7ea6-41ef-bff3-e9a08dec1330\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9c085ee5-f066-46bd-b2e5-150804da461f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">----------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5af27d22-467b-45aa-a3d9-f0c3e8a40773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-adcac6ad-162a-48c4-b293-3685dc74820b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">A  Type</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2553b93a-b1bf-4494-ae53-7580d0dc8cc6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3e063c10-1827-4e12-b2aa-787046a4fef0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">----------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-744f6d80-2534-410c-be94-cadc4fb152ec\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9a79279a-685a-4e47-a2d2-c0aeae943317\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a3a2dc92-1062-4715-b56c-3a9d680b700f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0fffe8e4-d265-4a89-962e-391038b97163\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·프로필 사진 : 해상도 좋은 이미지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c75b5a41-b61c-4763-b983-260126cc244e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-76346e9a-f83b-47a5-922f-c83f44c36fb3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·로고 : png, ai, pdf만 가능</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-91a18ae9-3b2d-4d92-bbd5-5a516bd2a459\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2b58cb5e-50b4-4928-8a1d-e1c95cb57c2c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·회사정보 : 각 센터의 정보를 보내줍니다. 여기에는 센터명, 주소, 이메일, 상담 시간, 운영시간 등등이 담겨 있을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35787b19-da5b-474f-bc2e-755fc08a4b15\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-61710835-67df-41d4-a7e0-12a1bcab759a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7d2ae688-e4ca-48d2-a4a9-8b7621af27e2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-257b416a-4937-46f6-bcda-3b8bdd8a7d79\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·메인타이틀 문구 : 약 2줄 내용기재 &gt;&gt;&gt; 자신의 특징이 되는 눈에 띄는 문구를 작성해 보내주시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6aea3b2-7679-4495-8164-e89a43674ec5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c404cc3a-0732-47dc-8b48-f800255f7cc2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eee6198e-f1a4-40f6-8bbe-14fb3e3dda00\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-126e91e5-7b3c-410d-b298-58d6836ee8a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·키워드 : 3가지 약 2줄(50자 이내) &gt;&gt;&gt; 자신만의 키워드를 적어서 보내주시면 맞춰서 디자인합니다. 예시로 적힌 내용의 글자와 제목을 참고하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8c15a3fa-001d-4c32-97fd-ad07b3ca7a14\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-adc4c2ad-d08b-4ad4-847b-be3b9541d8ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d92124aa-a296-4223-9708-b119fd741aee\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b0c74081-41c3-4c08-a54e-7f198b1b9304\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·회사(센터명/직책)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2ed4e5dd-3a21-4425-901d-a7d84673222d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-40584ad3-f159-43ee-8c20-7222d3ab6ee6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·이름</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-92434d78-7549-488b-99fc-acfaea24cdcd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-339fe810-67af-4aae-a346-b7f7233d8bd9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·핸드폰 번호</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-69339fa7-36dc-460e-bca6-fe52b8db1e55\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a7656aea-7513-4d7a-a2b5-6759ac100d2d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·프로필 &gt;&gt;&gt; 주요 프로필을 적어서 보내주시되 간단하게 약 10중 내외로 적어주시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c396864d-2fbe-4d2d-a9a3-342184c0372d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0a2ff094-f7ff-4b19-977a-fa7fb06aa253\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· QR : QR코드가 있으면 삽입 가능</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc55ced7-9271-49ef-a6d4-9726f41cc17a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a6a08f25-f114-4c7c-b493-8871086e4f71\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223527277823/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-34258410-9d16-447a-bc11-d4467a24d71c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0be060a0-deb4-4a95-9c84-616b61cd2744\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5c071f92-6d2b-40ba-be75-dbb3394dbcef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">----------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c1fa4681-193d-4df6-8584-6686b8d990ff\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-099fb8d5-d5e3-470f-b640-52b14b57db1a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">B  Type</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9386203b-ee9c-41ae-8204-1057535c0584\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-766c3705-194a-4e89-b4a8-a579bab859f2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">----------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c8691364-1e81-4668-978f-a4d782e1bcc7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c58b74ee-af34-45c9-b7f8-f58c88504614\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-14593fd1-1686-4dbd-b80b-f7a03d1ba0f1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9979d7ce-2511-4a6b-b392-67ed39698687\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·회사정보 : 각 센터의 정보를 보내줍니다. 여기에는 센터명, 주소, 이메일, 상담 시간, 운영시간 등등이 담겨 있을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-63561db6-6a9a-4d66-9765-c4b7dfe4d3b6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-69f90162-5979-43b8-8cb9-abc3fa50309a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·로고 : png, ai, pdf만 가능</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ffa711d3-8736-4425-965d-2b80f74acc4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-90683b42-3992-4283-9448-c7c29e8808c0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2350baaa-0298-46c5-bb4c-896a40a4c54b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1c71394f-fe0d-4356-8b1c-fd3d6bf68acf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·타깃 : 주요 고객층 등 타깃 기재 &gt;&gt;&gt; 예시처럼 주요 타깃을 적을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-78827fef-15e2-4246-bad4-068333375446\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f56a39ee-ec0f-42e9-a595-297a86004e42\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·비전 : 영업 비전 등을 2줄로 요약해서 보내주시면 편집합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad03fd8e-bf57-4c26-ae28-598d57313c5a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-76599e2a-0c76-46bc-b049-c60f0639993e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fa5abcdd-43ca-42ca-bba5-6e07cf8ca7fe\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-eb8054e1-9e9a-474d-80c4-4327075e648c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·프로필 사진 : 해상도 좋은 이미지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0e6296a6-8a95-4f18-b77b-e6f83608e801\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-70082aaf-39ce-43e8-adab-479cb3b0cece\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·주요 프로필 : 주요 프로필을 적어서 텍스트로 보내주십시오. B 타입은 프로필을 가장 많이 넣고 사진도 크게 디자인된 템플릿입니다. 자신의 프로필이 많은 분에게 권장합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0b1032fc-03f5-4382-9107-b9d1bf344490\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5faec381-483b-4ace-b1b6-5883b5d9977e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4655882b-005b-4817-ac5d-b4a7368bbce8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1eb0832b-9958-4a35-96f8-39b6c9daf150\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·회사(센터명/직책)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-40ce15c8-b419-4a9f-b435-bd3a4743eac5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-72c3d60e-ed6a-4b0d-a6a9-48d1d30a7172\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·이름</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3eb1a754-ba63-44b0-bded-bc3be0cde64d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-cecfdbf9-6c99-4e14-ab45-a0f1049bc884\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·핸드폰 번호</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6c73c9ee-247a-4fa9-81f1-9eea07d8a91e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a7a1e5e-043d-407b-8a35-f68261de920a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223527277823/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-02a4fe82-8fe0-4782-a29e-2d63710b0bbf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-407ccc17-62bf-4778-bf8c-c0ca8032b33a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-6d7e3cac-6cbc-4a5e-9ef5-1e1ab4e10e3e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">----------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e73b7c24-71a6-4384-8aa8-157bf300bd71\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a6ca04ac-510a-41b3-b0dd-18cfbc26138a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">C Type</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-968fbce7-80dd-44ca-b77a-181512f343d5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-42a9e310-3bf0-4952-b25f-6bf1acc79e6e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">----------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c59c817e-c12d-4fc0-856d-d3015ae70a23\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3a2f2ef9-2988-47d9-80b8-d4cf58b7d342\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28fb2941-954d-4915-8ffa-b095afdc043b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-51be6b3f-83a7-437d-a0f9-21408bda4b32\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·타이틀 : 자사 슬로건 6~8자 이내 &gt;&gt;&gt; 자신의 업종을 간단하게 적을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b22c1d72-3d62-4c63-bac1-53d00c8a87c5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7544eb04-13ab-4e69-9981-864fa4fbc47b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·슬로건 : 핵심적인 것 2줄로 압축해서 텍스트로 전달</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2e6166f7-844b-426d-8dcb-137fb3e6059d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7412a8f0-39dd-4244-8313-cd39b4bd3114\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a616182f-72e4-4e9f-a2c5-86faa1372177\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-082a0b91-4ef9-418b-af2a-ed1aab57735d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·회사/로고 : png, ai, pdf만 가능</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4f927a2c-dc71-4808-8882-60cc60b31166\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1942d8f3-c06b-4b37-b36d-b82d00c7a6ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·운영시간/상담시간 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6bab7733-6856-433f-85a6-78164b481a55\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3ad3f26a-0b67-48fb-a76b-dca127f2789b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·주소</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4d18cde3-ea9e-41aa-acc3-01bca2a6af22\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ce718159-3f0f-449d-b1a5-65efee51d8cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·회사 전화번호/팩스번호</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4479decc-8fff-4a04-8866-cf3ffc9ae9a7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-233232eb-5873-4895-b736-34c7c74936bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·이메일/sns/홈페이지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d85823aa-c682-4813-b1e0-c1f93b978161\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e0f53f8e-73ed-41c5-970f-c9d7bb35be79\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4f39c75f-56f2-4ce1-a235-a9d6ee30707d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ce36f08f-48aa-4ff5-a77d-ed320b4eeef9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·주요 약력/프로필 : 주요 약력/프로필을 적어서 텍스트로 보내주십시오. C 타입은 사진을 통이미지로 깔고 그 위에 디자인을 하고 싶은 분께 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4627b67f-aba5-4753-a1bf-71e16910702b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3d517c01-5f19-4ee9-9015-ca706098499a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-962d7de8-24f9-49d8-b9b2-2bd1544dd918\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f38a6ca0-efac-4841-ada2-abb751da54ea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·이름/회사/직급</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cb64a4f0-4fff-466a-a539-688f7b8669de\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9266c63d-c217-4f58-8774-0f1f3b5b3712\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·핸드폰 번호</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d56866b6-c6a2-4d00-924b-c51419550941\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c70423ca-7900-4799-81e8-a675e89796db\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-753666f2-bc4b-4704-86b2-5949bb4db158\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1d5aa363-db3c-42c7-be08-4c70e4252a65\" style=\"color:#555555;\">·프로필 사진 : 해상도 좋은 이미지 &gt;&gt;&gt; C 타입은 전체에 풀로 이미지 사진을 깔고 그 위에 디자인을 합니다. 세로형 이미지나 기타 통 이미지로 해상도 좋은 이미지를 보내주십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4063de61-4e0b-43c4-837c-7eaaa4388682\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7ab9256e-b2bd-4936-8a0f-8aee16884b62\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-efff71b8-4f06-4262-951f-28c2a91a86c4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-19af15f0-16b4-46e7-9a87-0cb4040246d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· QR : QR코드가 있으면 삽입 가능</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7acce7a2-9dc3-4508-8eb1-b74260dd1891\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-a493b79b-c7f9-4f4d-978d-a61f9b0cc9d2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223527277823/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fe99018c-7b46-47b2-be33-dc56b7ee882a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e12fa336-6c7f-469c-b212-7d9ffef7c197\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기존의 템플릿 디자인이 아닌 것으로도 새롭게 디자인 작업이 가능한가요?</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-69d14546-02ee-4be1-a7b0-e0b7b986a0e6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a354caa3-1331-4d78-b2ba-3f2a26f29825\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니에서는 당연히 새로운 디자인으로 작업이 가능합니다. 다만 자료와 비용 기간이 추가될 수 있습니다. 하지만 내용에 따라 금액이 변경될 수 있지만 큰 비용이 청구되지 않습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ccd659b6-a9e5-4dfd-bef7-13fb38672edf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3d408465-b5dc-4984-95af-3828a0f27afd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-165c659f-5923-411d-b966-15916c133fb9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a8d575fe-2ac2-492c-9d1d-9b0e700b62bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">별도의 디자인이 요구되는 경우</span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a4bb4387-c351-48fd-9ba5-9d9d1cfbcded\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d7e9c3fd-2f49-4461-8d4b-3530c9e81223\" style=\"color:#555555;\">새로운 사이즈나 사진 보정을 원하는 경우</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc03f0c1-90a8-4c8c-893f-d5f3afb09673\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-295c3d84-b372-4d9e-82db-2fc85e25af77\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특별한 문구나 기존에 디자인 예시를 가지고 있는 경우</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5546b857-ad27-4aa2-a130-b7c4fd455a89\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-17a839b5-cd1f-47bc-b229-368659bad426\" style=\"color:#555555;\">별도의 완전 색다른 컬러나 디자인 레이아웃을 원하는 경우</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-be16afc1-b8a2-485d-84a0-be79d00ee6d6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8cdfaff5-3750-4e31-86b0-7aa291d59908\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b8127771-defe-458f-9768-37907d494f0e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-aebe3dcf-5da1-4cd6-8f8a-9de89bfa6455\" style=\"color:#555555;\">프로필 명함이 궁금하신 분은 언제든지 문의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2acda31a-8df6-4003-b0bf-5d405a7c8387\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f0eef57f-095b-47e5-9923-362d18c127bd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f0b51052-f5ad-43f6-a923-bda3f18df7fb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5332efc0-3102-4c7a-8b4d-f08a6af1c1d6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">ps. 지금 이 글을 보시는 분은 홍보 문자를 보고 들어오신 경우가 많을 겁니다. 정성껏 보낸 홍보문구가 불편하셨다면 죄송합니다. 홍보성 문구가 귀찮으시면 미리 사전에 알려주세요. 보내지 않겠습니다. 감사합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ceb418e9-b46b-4abf-ba13-c72c30a354d1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-126cedec-1b5b-4fd8-8e4c-2c8f41d81669\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f6575efb-c8a4-4e23-b21d-5944fc6bc302\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d2510f36-013e-4d9d-9e2a-a26842d54346\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-da98f7d1-dfe4-4bd3-a164-3b5794ade15e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc0a6415-fa29-44ac-b427-18fea28c5412\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-03fbe687-9047-4bf1-ab29-26fe2c8a8e26\" style=\"color:#555555;\">카톡으로 연락 주시면 성실히 답변해 드리겠습니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}